right at the tip of the sacrum bone, at the coccyx,

26
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:54,800
and so it relates to the pelvic plexus, the sacral plexus,

27
00:01:54,960 --> 00:01:59,720
the coccygeal plexus and one other plexus that

28
