It can be fixed, of course. This is the whole point that

83
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:41,840
Self-Realization, that each of these centers

84
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:47,000
can be managed in such a way that any damage can be neutralized

85
00:05:47,200 --> 00:05:52,000
and in such a way that the spiritual ascent can be a growing,

86
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:54,960
tremendous force within each one of us.

87
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:58,400
But the damage is there especially in the west.

88
