00:12:53,800 --> 00:12:59,600
if She is here to takes us through that next stage in our evolution

193
00:12:59,800 --> 00:13:02,800
just keep yourself in that frame of mind where

194
00:13:02,960 --> 00:13:05,720
it's a spontaneous happening that has to take place.

195
00:13:05,920 --> 00:13:10,240
It's the terminal point, if you like, in the principle of evolution

196
00:13:10,440 --> 00:13:13,240
as epitomized by this center here.

197
00:13:13,440 --> 00:13:15,120
And so if She speaks forcefully

198
00:13:15,320 --> 00:13:18,760
about the qualities of a loving mother,

199
00:13:18,960 --> 00:13:22,760
if She speaks strongly about the nature of family life

